      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，用CreateOrderCMD触发到OrderPending状态。那Processing之后除了正常完成，有没有异常分支？比如处理失败的情况？",
