      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：Vault到Pending，Pending到Processing，Processing到Completed。同时把Error状态加上，Processing用MarkOrderCompleteCMD连到Error。",
